# Stat with Spectrwm

A small dynamic tiling window manager for X11 written in C and configured with a text configuration file. *spectrwm* is simple and easy to use.

## Brief Keybindings

The MODKEY4 = Windows Key

| Keys        | Action               |
| :---------- | :------------------- |
| MOD+Enter   | Open Terminal (bash) |
| MOD+q       | Close Window         |
| MOD+Shit+r  | Restart Spectrwm     |
| MOD+r       | Ranger Filemanager   |
| MOD+v       | Open Vim             |
| MOD+0       | System Account       |

For more keybindings check the /.config/spectrwm/spectrwm.conf file.

(press q to exit)

